</td>
<td class='code-content word-gray'><span class='code-line'>// This is a manifest file that'll be compiled into application.js, which will include all the files</span>
<span class='code-line'>// listed below.</span>
<span class='code-line'>//</span>
<span class='code-line'>// Any JavaScript/Coffee file within this directory, lib/assets/javascripts, vendor/assets/javascripts,</span>
<span class='code-line'>// or any plugin's vendor/assets/javascripts directory can be referenced here using a relative path.</span>
<span class='code-line'>//</span>
<span class='code-line'>// It's not advisable to add code directly here, but if you do, it'll appear at the bottom of the</span>
<span class='code-line'>// compiled file.</span>
<span class='code-line'>//</span>
<span class='code-line'>// Read Sprockets README (https://github.com/rails/sprockets#sprockets-directives) for details</span>
